snippet.title: Hell is Us | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Learn more: https://hell-is-us.com/

In an isolated country ravaged by civil war, uncover the secrets of your past and confront the mysterious disaster that has struck the region. Embark on a true adventure that explores the dark side of human nature.   

#HELLisUS will be available on PlayStation 5, Xbox Series and PC in 2023.
-------------------------------
For news about the game, you can also follow us on: 

Twitter ► https://twitter.com/HELLisUSgame
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/HELLisUSgame
